# Project Boss — Coding Standards

## Backend (Express + TypeScript + Prisma)

### Arsitektur WAJIB: Class-Based dengan Base Class Inheritance

```
routes → Controller (extends BaseController) → Service (extends BaseService) → Repository (class static)
```

### Aturan Utama:
1. Controller WAJIB extends `BaseController` dari `src/controller/base.controller.ts`
2. Service WAJIB extends `BaseService` dari `src/service/base.service.ts`
3. Repository = satu-satunya layer yang boleh akses `db` (Prisma)
4. Service TIDAK BOLEH langsung akses Prisma
5. Controller TIDAK BOLEH punya business logic
6. Response selalu pakai `ResponseUtil`
7. Error handling pakai `AppError`
8. Validasi input pakai Zod schema di middleware

### Contoh Controller:
```typescript
import { Request, Response } from "express";
import { BaseController } from "./base.controller";
import { ProductService } from "../service/product.service";

class ProductController extends BaseController {
  getAll = this.handler(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {
    const data = await ProductService.getAll(req.query);
    return this.paginated(res, data.data, data.page, data.limit, data.total);
  });

  create = this.handler(async (req: Request, res: Response) => {
    const result = await ProductService.create(req.body);
    return this.success(res, result, 201);
  });
}
export const productController = new ProductController();
```

### Contoh Service:
```typescript
import { BaseService } from "./base.service";
import { ProductRepository } from "../repositories/product.repository";

export class ProductService extends BaseService {
  static async getById(id: string) {
    const product = await ProductRepository.findById(id);
    if (!product) this.notFound("Produk tidak ditemukan");
    return product;
  }

  static async create(data: any) {
    return ProductRepository.create(data);
  }
}
```

### Contoh Repository:
```typescript
import { db } from "../config/prisma";

export class ProductRepository {
  static async findById(id: string) {
    return db.product.findUnique({ where: { id } });
  }
}
```

Referensi lengkap: `.github/instructions/backend-coding-standards.md`

## Dashboard & Frontend (Next.js)
- API calls lewat `lib/apis/` atau service class yang extends `BaseService`
- Data fetching pakai React Query hooks di `hooks/api/`
- UI pakai shadcn/ui components
- Form pakai `reuseable-form.tsx` (react-hook-form + zod)
